Map - Class in map
This class uses nodes, MapStreet, ResidenceNode and MapBuilding to represent the background map of the application.

Creates a new BackGroundMap

Creates a simple Building without text label but with customized style
MapBuilding(String, Shape, Color, double, Color) - Constructor for class map.MapBuilding

MapStreet - Class in map
This class is a graphical representation of a street in the map
MapStreet(Path) - Constructor for class map.MapStreet
Creates a Street with no label and default style
MapStreet(String, Path) - Constructor for class map.MapStreet

MapStreet(String, Path, int) - Constructor for class map.MapStreet

MapStreet(String, Path, double) - Constructor for class map.MapStreet
